#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.140"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.140:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.140:0.2"
msgid "14. Yodhājīvavagga "
msgstr "14. A Warrior "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.140:0.3"
msgid "140. Assakhaḷuṅkasutta "
msgstr "140. A Wild Colt "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.140:1.1"
msgid "“Tayo ca, bhikkhave, assakhaḷuṅke desessāmi tayo ca purisakhaḷuṅke. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you about three wild colts and three wild people. "

msgctxt "an3.140:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.140:1.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an3.140:1.4"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.288, sc2
msgctxt "an3.140:2.1"
msgid "“Katame ca, bhikkhave, tayo assakhaḷuṅkā? "
msgstr "“What are the three wild colts? "

msgctxt "an3.140:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco assakhaḷuṅko javasampanno hoti; na vaṇṇasampanno, na ārohapariṇāhasampanno. "
msgstr "One wild colt is fast, but not beautiful or well proportioned. "

msgctxt "an3.140:2.3"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, ekacco assakhaḷuṅko javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca; na ārohapariṇāhasampanno. "
msgstr "Another wild colt is fast and beautiful, but not well proportioned. "

msgctxt "an3.140:2.4"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, ekacco assakhaḷuṅko javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca. "
msgstr "While another wild colt is fast, beautiful, and well proportioned. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.140:2.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo assakhaḷuṅkā. "
msgstr "These are the three wild colts. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.140:3.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, tayo purisakhaḷuṅkā? "
msgstr "And what are the three wild people? "

msgctxt "an3.140:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco purisakhaḷuṅko javasampanno hoti; na vaṇṇasampanno, na ārohapariṇāhasampanno. "
msgstr "One wild person is fast, but not beautiful or well proportioned. "

msgctxt "an3.140:3.3"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, ekacco purisakhaḷuṅko javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca; na ārohapariṇāhasampanno. "
msgstr "Another wild person is fast and beautiful, but not well proportioned. "

msgctxt "an3.140:3.4"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, ekacco purisakhaḷuṅko javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca. "
msgstr "While another wild person is fast, beautiful, and well proportioned. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an3.140:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, purisakhaḷuṅko javasampanno hoti; na vaṇṇasampanno na ārohapariṇāhasampanno? "
msgstr "And how is a wild person fast, but not beautiful or well proportioned? "

msgctxt "an3.140:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant truly understands: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’. "

msgctxt "an3.140:4.3"
msgid "Idamassa javasmiṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "This is how they’re fast, I say. "

#. VAR: saṃsādeti → saṃhīreti (mr)
msgctxt "an3.140:4.4"
msgid "Abhidhamme kho pana abhivinaye pañhaṃ puṭṭho saṃsādeti, no vissajjeti. "
msgstr "But when asked a question about the teaching or training, they falter without answering. "

msgctxt "an3.140:4.5"
msgid "Idamassa na vaṇṇasmiṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "This is how they’re not beautiful, I say. "

msgctxt "an3.140:4.6"
msgid "Na kho pana lābhī hoti cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ. "
msgstr "And they don’t receive robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick. "

msgctxt "an3.140:4.7"
msgid "Idamassa na ārohapariṇāhasmiṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "This is how they’re not well proportioned, I say. "

msgctxt "an3.140:4.8"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, purisakhaḷuṅko javasampanno hoti; na vaṇṇasampanno, na ārohapariṇāhasampanno. "
msgstr "This is how a wild person is fast, but not beautiful or well proportioned. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.289, sc5
msgctxt "an3.140:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, purisakhaḷuṅko javasampanno ca hoti vaṇṇasampanno ca; na ārohapariṇāhasampanno? "
msgstr "And how is a wild person fast and beautiful, but not well proportioned? "

